<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About & Contact - VP Blog</title>
    <style>
        /* Import Google Font */
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@200;300;400;600;700&display=swap');

        /* Root Variables */
        :root {
            --black: #1c1c1c;
            --gray: #7E7E7E;
            --gray-light: #E4E4E4;
            --red: #b30000;
            --font-size-base: 1rem;
            --font-size-md: clamp(1.25rem, 0.61vw + 1.1rem, 1.58rem);
            --font-size-lg: clamp(1.56rem, 1vw + 1.31rem, 2.11rem);
            --border-radius: 10px;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            color: var(--black);
            font-size: var(--font-size-base);
            background-color: #FAF5EE;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        section {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        ul li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        input, textarea {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1rem;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
        }

        button {
            background-color: var(--black);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: var(--gray);
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--gray);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>About Us</h1>
        </header>
        <section>
            <h2>Welcome to VP Blog</h2>
            <p>Your go-to destination for insightful articles, expert opinions, and engaging stories.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Who We Are</h2>
            <p>At <strong>VP Blog</strong>, we are passionate about sharing knowledge. Our team of writers, researchers, and enthusiasts work together to bring you well-researched and up-to-date content.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Quality Content:</strong> Well-researched and easy-to-understand articles.</li>
                <li><strong>User-Focused Approach:</strong> Content tailored to help readers make informed decisions.</li>
                <li><strong>Regular Updates:</strong> Fresh articles to keep you engaged and inspired.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        
    </div>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 VP Blog. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
